https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b70c3ba6b6a0f680a246d4df0faf29650b8d47a","tid":1605472,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"係咪咁樣是鳩但出個地圖炮sms<br />\n咁聽日就全香港戒嚴?<br />\n行出去就後果自負既意思?<br />\n<br />\n係唔係應該都要推廣出去俾全世界知道?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd74f26f18606ff4729b93fa83ef1e426863c0c","tid":1605472,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"之前有post話登記拒收信訊名冊就唔會收到<br />\n宜家都仲收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069c863d23b650925c54d06b297e5b5e0f3333dc","tid":1605472,"uid":70771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"次鳩次都係咁, 冇乜意思<br />\n利申: 應該同大家一樣都係第三次收到"},{"pid":"885ea0e7d78c29f7195507f2e529fe96ee50780e","tid":1605472,"uid":299360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"收到 然後屌左佢老母"}]}